{"title":"我们的岁月","authors":["常敬竹"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常敬竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天边的云很高很蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是赶路的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬季风雕凿的艰辛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次被拉长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮湿与泥泞已成为记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时，我们正扬起青铜的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤所有的后来者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被风雪肆意地嘲弄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被太阳热辣辣地亲吻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信念脱了一层又一层皮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可生命依然深一脚浅一脚地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顽强前行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生的码头拥挤不堪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泊满无边的双帆船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"视线之外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千支铜风铃在幽幽诉说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有失意秋叶般沉重跌落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭岁月如何超重，我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也决不背弃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当初那次真诚的许诺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思维在密封的隧道里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲击着各个角落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻求理解　这时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后有许多死去的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一一复活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次同太阳对话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是没有结果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只知道我们的心依然很热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们想因此悄然出走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同一群陌生人活在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让从前的错误生辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让从前的荣誉死去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者，花一生时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"购买一次反醒"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}